re). <br>
After dieing the last time and I had 2 eyes, I decided to come back later when I could handle these bad boys a little better.<br>
So I traveled to Timorous deep and went to the island next to Ogre isle and killed Falen Iksar. They were high blue and I could take 2 of them out before I had to med back up.<br>
That is currently where I am and I will post more an this later.<br>
P.S. I was lvl 18 at the time I was doing this.FYI<br>
